BIG NEWS!!!  I have a brand new children’s book out!! It’s titled - “As You Grow” and it’s part of the Freedom Island Book Club by BRAVE Books. 

My book teaches kids about Biblical wisdom and the importance of relying on Biblical principles through all seasons of life. With games and activities in the back of my book, the kids in your life are sure to be blessed by this book! 

Our children’s morality is ingrained by the age of 10. We need resources to help establish a strong moral foundation and the Freedom Island Book Club is the perfect tool to do just that. 

When you subscribe your family will receive a new book each month that teaches an important pro-God, pro-America lesson which parents and grandparents need more than ever right now to help teach their children and grandchildren good morals and values. 

Click the link in bio to learn more about the BRAVE Books book of the month subscription

Good people are supposed to be creating the culture for our children. When we fail to do that, we create a vacuum, and then moral evil, rottenness, and badness come in, and that’s what is coming after our kids more than ever before.  
We, As parents and grandparents, need tools to help teach the next generation to love freedom, seek truth, embody a humble spirit, live compassion-filled lives, and most importantly, be BRAVE.  
@bravebooks.us offers a monthly subscription to the Freedom Island Series in which your family will receive a new book each month that teaches a different lesson. Lessons on the value of life, free speech, family, why the Constitution is so important, and now in my book, learning wisdom in the various seasons of life!  
This is such an amazing gift that is sure to bless the loved ones in your life!

God's Reminder to Us

The National Monument to the Forefathers stands as a solemn reminder that the foundation of this great nation was not solely the work of human hands, but a divine design guided by the hand of God. As an intricately sculpted tribute in Plymouth, Massachusetts, this monument pays homage to the early Pilgrims and their enduring faith. Its towering figures symbolize virtues such as Faith, Liberty, and Morality, serving as a testament to the spiritual underpinnings of America's founding. In its presence, one can find a profound message: that it was God's providence that laid the cornerstone of this nation, shaping its destiny through the unwavering dedication of those who believed in His guidance. The National Monument to the Forefathers thus serves as a timeless reminder of the spiritual essence woven into the very fabric of the United States.
